<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/28266234-7jane"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1391265302i/28266234._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
